OL,3,C'A lifetime of grief': Parents'
OL,4,Cwarning after son killed in hit-and-run
OL,6,FITV West Country's Jacquie Bird has
OL,7,Fbeen speaking to Mark and Helen Saltern
OL,9,FA family from Cornwall have warned of
OL,10,Fthe dangers of drink and drug driving
OL,11,Ffive years after their son was killed
OL,12,Fin a hit-and-run.
OL,14,FRyan Saltern, 31, from St Teath, died
OL,15,Fafter being struck by a vehicle.
OL,17,FHis parents, Mark and Helen, have
OL,18,Fcampaigned for tougher sentences for
OL,19,Fthose convicted of causing death by
OL,20,Fdangerous driving.
