OL,3,C'A lifetime of grief': Parents'
OL,4,Cwarning after son killed in hit-and-run
OL,6,FBut now the pair are also hoping to
OL,7,Fraise awareness of the consequences of
OL,8,Fdrink or drug driving, as part of
OL,9,FNational Road Victim Month.
OL,11,FMark said: "It's a lifetime of grief.
OL,12,Fthe first thing you think of in the
OL,13,Fmorning and the last thing at night.
OL,14,FAnd that's every day."
OL,16,FHelen added: "And there's always an
OL,17,Fempty chair isn't there, at family
OL,18,Foccasions, But we carry him in our
OL,19,Fhearts and he will never ever be
OL,20,Fforgotten."
