OL,3,C'A lifetime of grief': Parents'
OL,4,Cwarning after son killed in hit-and-run
OL,6,FLast year, more than 700 people were
OL,7,Fkilled or injured on roads in Devon
OL,8,Fand Cornwall.
OL,10,FNow the Saltern's are calling for a
OL,11,Fchange in the law to make it a more
OL,12,Fserious offence to drive away from the
OL,13,Fscene of a crash.
OL,15,FThe man who struck Ryan pleaded guilty
OL,16,Fto failing to stop and failing to
OL,17,Freport the accident.
