OL,6,FHe received a four-month jail
OL,7,Fsentence, which was suspended for a
OL,8,Fyear, disqualified from driving for 12
OL,9,Fmonths and given an evening curfew for
OL,10,Ffour months.
OL,12,FThe Saltern family are also creating a
OL,13,Froom at their home near Bodmin for
OL,14,Ffamilies who've lost a loved one to
OL,15,Froad crime in their son's memory,
OL,16,Fcalled Ry's Haven.
