OL,3,C'A lifetime of grief': Parents'
OL,4,Cwarning after son killed in hit-and-run
OL,6,FDevon and Cornwall Police is part of
OL,7,FVision Zero, a campaign that aims to
OL,8,Freduce the number of serious injury
OL,9,Fand fatal crashes on the region's
OL,10,Froads to zero by 2030.
OL,12,FActing Chief Constable Jim Colwell
OL,13,Fsaid: "Lawful, law-abiding, innocent
OL,14,Fpeople get in a car, set off on a
OL,15,Fjourney and then on the odd occasion,
OL,16,Fthey make a really poor decision.
